    "README.md": [
      "# Ultraverse NFT Marketplace",
      "",
      "Ultraverse is a multi page React marketplace project I built with a much bigger focus on front end engineering than just themed visuals.",
      "",
      "What I care about most in this project is not the NFT topic by itself. It is the amount of real interface work behind it. I built routed pages, API driven sections, list to detail relationships, author profile views, reusable loading states, filters, countdown logic, interactive follow behavior, and a cleaner overall user flow across the app.",
      "",
      "This is the kind of project I like showing to recruiters and potential clients because it says more about how I build than what category the product sits in.",
      "",
      "## What I Built",
      ""
